{"tid":133413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警啟德郵輪碼頭演習　反同性戀刀匪「斬傷」十多人","createTime":"2017-02-24T14:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T15:08:58.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f5899906c2d78f21aaded28426846ee297e94a","tid":133413,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170224/s00001/1487939480074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170224%2Fs00001%2F1487939480074&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=65324727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170224%2Fs00001%2F1487939480074&h=d557beea\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170224/s00001/1487939480074</a><br />\n<br />\n回歸20周年臨近，警方東九龍總區今早在啟德郵輪碼頭反恐演習，近百名來自東九龍衝鋒隊、機動部隊及反恐特勤隊成員參與。演習模擬在郵輪碼頭發生大規模斬人事件，警方趕至並與「匪徒」駁火，最終將「匪徒」制服。<br />\n<br />\n演習今早約10時半開始，先有3名由警員扮演的持刀「匪徒」，在郵輪碼頭地面將兩名途人斬傷，並在「行兇」時，發表針對同性戀的言論。碼頭保安員見狀報警，3名「匪徒」逃至天台花園，並繼續斬傷十多人。大批衝鋒隊員趕至，與「匪徒」短暫駁火，並將「匪徒」制服。<br />\n<br />\n演習警員其後移師碼頭一樓停車場，並模擬警方接報有可疑車輛，上前截查時遇到兩名重火力「悍匪」還擊。警方出動反恐特勤隊，並與「悍匪」來回駁火多響，最終將「悍匪」擊斃。演習至中午前完結，據悉是次為恆常演練，東九龍總區指揮官麥國兆亦有到場觀察。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，警隊不時會進行常規演練，以令人員更專業及有效地執行職務，應付突發事件。"},{"pid":"29eba64f6cd7000ae1211a7a08a46eea4cf91418","tid":133413,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4098285e229145756ef8fde383fea0a2b54735fe","tid":133413,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"幾時演習有人係街大叫屌你老母,然後出動SDU?"},{"pid":"8021358d67ec07ea5a37c7843b67470e53af4393","tid":133413,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>演習今早約10時半開始，先有3名由警員扮演的持刀「匪徒」，在郵輪碼頭地面將兩名途人斬傷，並在「行兇」時，<span style=\"color: red;\">發表針對同性戀的言論。</span>碼頭保安員見狀報警，3名「匪徒」逃至天台花園，並繼續斬傷十多人。大批衝鋒隊員趕至，與「匪徒」短暫駁火，並將「匪徒」</blockquote><br />\n世界大戰抹黑宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2310ea9a950e343f2ab865e65d609b4b810855d","tid":133413,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"仲流過人地打war game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de713aab3b7294f7c9f69a625cf22a0da1cf5140","tid":133413,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"斬斬吓人又駁火？"},{"pid":"ddcc296445981f2629ddb4d82827cd87035f00b8","tid":133413,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"點解搞個演習都要set個咁撚奇怪嘅故事背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046715c27be285e5ff4db4e6a2a86ca4c54a968e","tid":133413,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"成件事唔合理<br />\n<br />\n點解D  匪徒有槍, 但要用刀斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0f963ba8647359b131e0abf28a409f289f111b","tid":133413,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解搞個演習都要set個咁撚奇怪嘅故事背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一路斬,  一路叫:「死gay佬, 死未」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}